@startuml
' @id(SEQ-WHOLE-MAP-ACCUMULATE)
' @ref(USE-WHOLE-MAP)
'
' Objective-side runtime flow of the whole-map accumulation that
' /mdd-cycle performs as part of its Close step. There is no separate
' re-derivation pass and no render-time fold: the persisted .mdd/map/
' tree IS the net, maintained one cheap CycleDiff application per cycle.
'
' @desc(SEQ-WHOLE-MAP-ACCUMULATE, "How /mdd-cycle's Close step folds a closed cycle's CycleDiff into the persisted per-concept .mdd/map/ tree (added @ids copied with @cycle provenance, removed dropped, unchanged keep prior provenance), refreshes manifest.yml, snapshots to .mdd/cycles/<N>/whole/, and hands off to /mdd-render to rasterize .mdd/map/**.")
title Accumulate the whole-map baseline at cycle close (objective)

participant "/mdd-cycle\n(Close step)" as Close
database ".mdd/cycles/<N>/\nbefore/, after/" as Snap
collections "CycleDiff per\ntouched concept" as Diff
database ".mdd/map/\n<kind>/<name>.puml\n+ manifest.yml" as Map
participant "/mdd-render" as Render

note over Close
  Runs only after parity closed and the cycle's
  current/ -> after/ snapshot + each
  <diagram>.diff.puml are already written.
  Whole-map accumulation reuses that same diff.
end note

Close -> Snap : read before/ and after/ for cycle N
Close -> Diff : CycleDiff(@id keys) per concept\n(added / removed / unchanged)

loop for each concept <kind>/<name> in after/
  alt .mdd/map/<kind>/<name>.puml absent
    Close -> Map : create from after/ content;\ntag every @id ' @cycle(<ID>,<N>)
  else whole-map file exists
    Close -> Map : insert added @ids (+elements)\nfrom after/, tag ' @cycle(<ID>,<N>)
    Close -> Map : delete removed @ids and\ntheir elements (net cancel — no ghost)
    note right of Map
      unchanged @ids keep their earlier
      ' @cycle(...) provenance.
    end note
  end
end

alt concept in before/ but not after/ (file deleted)
  Close -> Map : remove .mdd/map/<kind>/<name>.puml
end

Close -> Map : rewrite manifest.yml\n(version, last_cycle=N, generated_at, files)
Close -> Snap : copy .mdd/map/ -> .mdd/cycles/<N>/whole/
Close -> Render : /mdd-render
Render -> Map : rasterize .mdd/map/**.puml\n-> .mdd/rendered/map/**.svg

note over Map
  .mdd/map/ is an inspection artifact only.
  /mdd-validate, /mdd-review and the /mdd-cycle
  parity loop never read it (OCL-MAP-* constrain
  WholeMap but are not parity gates).
end note
@enduml
